- **SIDU (Sidus Space)**: Gap +21% (bars), low float ~10M (ratios), high short interest ~25% of float (ratios) with HARD difficulty (short data). Catalyst: Recent contracts + space sector hype. Sentiment spiking (Finnhub mentions +100% on X). Strategy: Buy >$5.25 break; target $6-7.
